<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.3">
<l>koṉṟēṉ palluyiraik kuṟikkōḷoṉṟi lāmaiyiṉāl</l>
<l>eṉṟē ṉumirantārk kiṉitākavu raittaṟiyēṉ</l>
<l>kuṉṟēy mēkamatir kuḷirmāmalai vēṅkaṭavā</l>
<l>aṉṟē vantaṭaintē ṉaṭiyēṉaiyāṭ koṇṭaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I killed many beings with a lack of any understanding;</l>
<l>I was not accustomed with speaking sweetly</l>
<l rend="indent">to those who entreated me, whatever the day.</l>
<l>You of great cool Tiruvēṅkaṭa Mountain, with hillock-like clouds thundering,</l>
<l>I, your slave, came [here and] took refuge;</l>
<l rend="indent">be gracious, receiving me, [your] servant, in service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
